The paper deals with querying in Fuzzy Databases, which is a subfield of Database Management Systems (cs.DB). It also involves the use of fuzzy linguistic summaries, which is a common technique in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the selection criteria for objects, which is related to Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Natural Language Processing (cs.CL).
